      "text": "cron script --> HERE\nsites directory --> HERE\nHERE --> words file --> words rollup\nHERE --> links file --> links rollup\nHERE --> sites file --> sites rollup --> sites total rollup\nHERE --> items file --> items rollup\nHERE --> plugins file --> plugins rollup\n"
